FIG. 1 is a flow diagram of a desalinization plant, showing the flow of water past the various filtration stations and the application of biofouling reduction treatment of this invention;


FIG. 2 is a flow diagram of a power plant located at a lake or ocean, showing the flow of cooling water past the various heat transfer units and the application of biofouling reduction treatment of this invention;


FIG. 3 is a flow diagram of an oilfield water injection facility, showing the flow of water past the various filtration stations and the application of biofouling reduction treatment of this invention; and


FIG. 4 is a flow diagram of a fire water system showing the flow of water to the sprinkler heads and deluge devices and the application of biofouling reduction treatment of this invention.
